{"id": "1239546141402595440", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185719465984413801", "author_name": "sayakakozuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "但是刚开始第一把也没扣", "timestamp": "2024-05-13T11:53:49.764000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1239547002895990804", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "1000以下時，除非遇到1000以上的，不然每場勝利都有額外拿分(固定+50)，然後輸的-5%(應該)", "timestamp": "2024-05-13T11:57:15.160000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1239548998486855681", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185719465984413801", "author_name": "sayakakozuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是这样想的：1000以上没机器人，总分数可以看做固定。分数只会来回转移并不涨，只有一直有上1000分的新韭菜（bushi）来不断增加这个总分数，大伙的分数才能做到一直涨。而1000分以下因为有机器人，所以我才说天梯可以看做所有人都靠（新玩家匹配到的）机器人涨分。", "timestamp": "2024-05-13T12:05:10.946000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1239549304536961075", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "新玩家0分打0分也是會拿分的，除非都只遇到人機", "timestamp": "2024-05-13T12:06:23.914000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1239549670770868318", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185719465984413801", "author_name": "sayakakozuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "那个可以忽略不计，只有每个人初始的50分，天梯总人数乘以50，没多少分", "timestamp": "2024-05-13T12:07:51.231000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1239549737561231411", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185719465984413801", "author_name": "sayakakozuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "大头还在机器人身上", "timestamp": "2024-05-13T12:08:07.155000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
